  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Sorcerer Bloodline</strong><br/><br/><p>Your family is destined for greatness in some way. Your birth could have been foretold in prophecy, or perhaps it occurred during an especially auspicious event, such as a solar eclipse. Regardless of your bloodline's origin, you have a great future ahead.</p><p><b>Class Skill: </b>Knowledge (history).</p><p><b>Bonus Spells: </b>alarm (3rd), blur (5th), protection from energy (7th), freedom of movement (9th), break enchantment (11th), mislead (13th), spell turning (15th), moment of prescience (17th), foresight (19th).</p><p><b>Bonus Feats: </b>Arcane Strike, Diehard, Endurance, Leadership, Lightning Reflexes, Maximize Spell, Skill Focus (Knowledge [history]), Weapon Focus.</p><p><b>Bloodline Arcana: </b>Whenever you cast a spell with a range of 'personal,' you gain a luck bonus equal to the spell's level on all your saving throws for 1 round.</p><p><b>Bloodline Powers: </b>You are destined for great things, and the powers that you gain serve to protect you.</p>",
